OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777449958
OL,3,CGang who tried to throw away car keys
OL,4,Cbefore arrest jailed for vehicle thefts
OL,6,FA gang of car thieves who stole high
OL,7,Fperformance vehicles in Surrey and
OL,8,FSussex have been jailed.
OL,10,FThe group targeted grey Audi RS
OL,11,Fvehicles at addresses in Stoneleigh in
OL,12,FSurrey and Copthorne in Sussex,
OL,13,Fbreaking into the owners' houses as
OL,14,Fthey slept to steal their car keys
OL,15,Fbefore driving off in them.
OL,17,FThey were caught when officers on
OL,18,Fpatrol spotted an unattended grey Audi
OL,19,FRS4 in Chipstead, Surrey, on the same
OL,20,Fday as one of the thefts had happened.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
