OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777449958
OL,3,CGang who tried to throw away car keys
OL,4,Cbefore arrest jailed for vehicle thefts
OL,6,FPolice checks revealed the
OL,7,Fregistration plates were cloned and
OL,8,Fofficers were still there when the
OL,9,Ffour offenders returned to the car.
OL,11,FThey ran away after seeing the
OL,12,Fofficers, but were captured after a
OL,13,Fshort chase on foot.
OL,15,FThree of the group were jailed on
OL,16,FFriday April 17 at Guildford Crown
OL,17,FCourt.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
