PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777449958
OL,3,CGang who tried to throw away car keys
OL,4,Cbefore arrest jailed for vehicle thefts
OL,6,FA 17-year-old boy, who cannot be named
OL,7,Ffor legal reasons, was sentenced in an
OL,8,Fearlier hearing at Staines
OL,9,FMagistrates' Court in February and
OL,10,Freceived a Youth Referral Order for 12
OL,11,Fmonths and a three-year Criminal
OL,12,FBehaviour Order.
OL,14,FHe was disqualified from driving for
OL,15,F16 months.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
