CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777449958
OL,3,CGang who tried to throw away car keys
OL,4,Cbefore arrest jailed for vehicle thefts
OL,6,FPC Joe Brown said: "During the foot
OL,7,Fchase they tried to throw away car
OL,8,Fkeys connecting them to this vehicle,
OL,9,Fbut these were recovered along with
OL,10,Fanother set belonging to a second
OL,11,Fstolen car.
OL,13,F"We know vehicle theft has increased
OL,14,Fbut we are working hard every day to
OL,15,Fidentify and catch the offenders who
OL,16,Fare targeting them."
